    "description": "Solve interesting puzzles, manipulate <strong>Shifting Blocks</strong> to your advantage, and be careful not to crush yourself!<br>The Shifting Dungeon has 40+ rooms to explore, all with an optional star to collect, totaling <strong>80+</strong> unique challenges.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/6f28c67dc085079ab39f68e7e87d09d1.poster.avif?t=1703029437\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/6f28c67dc085079ab39f68e7e87d09d1.webm?t=1703029437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/6f28c67dc085079ab39f68e7e87d09d1.mp4?t=1703029437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You take control of the robot character, He can strategically blow up nearby blocks by crushing himself, he will then safely rebuild himself again<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/c4b516341231ffca04b680ac75190bb8.poster.avif?t=1703029437\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/c4b516341231ffca04b680ac75190bb8.webm?t=1703029437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/c4b516341231ffca04b680ac75190bb8.mp4?t=1703029437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Use blocks to avoid dangerous <strong>lazers</strong>!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757360/extras/2e57359479429b132decba86921ac9a4.poster.avif?t=1703029437\" width=60